headline.main: Fish Is Called 'Dupe of Hitlerism,' Defends His War Stand in Debate; Dr. W.Y. Elliott Acts as Spokesman for Orange County Group Opposing Isolation -- Warwick School Hall Crowded

lead_paragraph: WARWICK, N.Y., Sept. 19 -- The home folk of this Orange County Republican township, many of whom have grown irked by Representative Hamilton Fish's isolationism, reverted tonight to an old-fashioned American custom. They called him home to meet an ardent anti-isolationist in debate in the high school auditorium on the issues of American participation in the war.
abstract: debate; Fish's Cong record attacked by Dr R Bradner
